{"tid":2510753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［極重要］【清算港大學生會】港大停止代收會費、停「管數」服務　收回會室等設施管理權","createTime":"2021-04-30T11:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T11:20:41.000Z","uid":371815,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"61cd9d28dcf1fc02645f255a911ac2ec49d07ef3","tid":2510753,"uid":371815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdS5ffmi8RjjkFzVcEtoLVSXMXDrGdRBmPJR3eo2uXR82?filename=FE0vqZz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFE0vqZz.png&h=f023249b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港大學教務長曾詠詩今日（30 日）向全體學生發信，宣布停止為港大學生會代收會費、不再向學生會提供財務管理服務，同時會對學生會正使用的辦公室及設施「執行管理權力」（enforce our management rights），收回港大學生會會室等設施管理權。<br />\n<br />\n信件語言為英文，指港大學生會是《社團條例》下註冊的獨立組織，為了糾正大學與學生會之間、針對法律責任問題的「長期矛盾」（protracted ambivalence），大學早前檢討向學生會提供的服務及安排，以作出「合適的風險管理」（appropriate risk management）。<br />\n<br />\n曾詠詩表示，大學決定停止為學生會代收會費、停止財務管理服務，並對學生會使用的辦公室「執行管理權力」，強調這些措施不會影響大學對支持課外活動、促進正面學習環境的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n港大：學生會趨政治化　大學非法外之地<br />\n<br />\n香港大學隨即發聲明，對學生會「偏激的言行予以强烈譴責」。發言人指，學生會近年行事日趨政治化，多次利用校園作為政治宣傳的平台，公開發表煽動性並可能涉及違法的言論，對大學作出失實指控，破壞多年來與校方建立的互信，令大學的整體利益和聲譽蒙損。<br />\n<br />\n發言人續指「大學不是法外之地」，指基本法作為香港法治的基石，在保障了大學學術自由、個人言論表達自由和結社自由的同時，也有保護國家安全的條文，大學亦有責任維護全體教職員和學生的福祉，「不能容忍作為獨立社團的學生會一方面利用學校提供的服務和場所，另一方面則漠視校方的勸喻和整體港大社群利益」。<br />\n<br />\n港大指，學生會「所作所為給大學帶來違法風險」，大學必須釐清與學生會之間的法律責任，並會因應情況在有需要時採取進一步措施。<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》月中點名批評港大學生會<br />\n<br />\n翻查報道，中國官媒《人民日報》本月中（18 日）發表評論，點名港大學生會是要切除的「毒瘤」，指港大學生會「已到了非管不可的時候」，評論又批評港大學生會本月中曾發聲明，「抹黑」大學推行國安教育是「斷送院校自主」、「愧對學士先賢」。（詳見另稿）<br />\n<br />\n而在《人民日報》發表評論後 12 日後，港大即宣布上文幾項封殺措施；港大隨即發表聲明，指學生會「所作所為給大學帶來違法風險」，必須釐清關係。<br />\n<br />\n校友張昆陽斥港大「失德」<br />\n<br />\n主打「國際線」、已流亡的前港大學生會評議會時事委員會委員張崑陽在網上發文，指作為曾服務學生會的港大舊生，譴責校方「失德之舉」，因港大近年屢次「賣港」以及打壓學生，他會致力游說外國視港大為中共政治工具及「統戰機關」，斷絕與港大官方合作，並制裁港大校方高層，拒絕他們在外國進行學術工作。（詳見報道）<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》正向香港大學查詢措施詳情，例如涉及由學生會管理的設施為何、目前停止何種財務管理服務等；《立場》同時正向港大學生會查詢，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n港大教務長信件全文如下：<br />\n<br />\nImportant message from the Registrar<br />\n<br />\nTo: All students of the University<br />\n<br />\nIn order to rectify the protracted ambivalence in the delineation of legal responsibilities between the University and the Hong Kong University Students&rsquo; Union (HKUSU), an independent organization registered under the Societies Ordinance of Hong Kong, the University has undertaken a review on the current services and arrangements made available to the HKUSU for appropriate risk management. It is now decided that the University will stop collecting membership fees on behalf of the HKUSU and providing financial management services for them, and will enforce our management rights over the offices and other facilities currently used by HKUSU. These measures will not affect the continued commitment of the University to facilitate and support extra-curricular activities on campus and foster a positive learning environment for all students.<br />\n<br />\n(Ms) Jeannie Tsang<br />\nRegistrar<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/清算學生會-港大停止代收會費-停-管數-服務-暗示收回會室等設施使用權/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B8%85%E7%AE%97%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E4%BB%A3%E6%94%B6%E6%9C%83%E8%B2%BB-%E5%81%9C-%E7%AE%A1%E6%95%B8-%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99-%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E%E6%9C%83%E5%AE%A4%E7%AD%89%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%AC%8A%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=7f38ee0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B8%85%E7%AE%97%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E4%BB%A3%E6%94%B6%E6%9C%83%E8%B2%BB-%E5%81%9C-%E7%AE%A1%E6%95%B8-%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99-%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E%E6%9C%83%E5%AE%A4%E7%AD%89%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%AC%8A%2F&h=41e46c1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/清算學生會-港大停止代收會費-停-管數-服務-暗示收回會室等設施使用權/</a><br />\n<br />\n咁大件事點解係連登可以一個post都冇"},{"pid":"903b4f22da92aa2f1642388981d5679c203fd1b4","tid":2510753,"uid":371815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9673546e7c8f914d13640fd9e816a5410fcd2245","tid":2510753,"uid":371815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb47a5d41be3847f95981864c37619a56b68d35","tid":2510753,"uid":371815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2574dc328f797912d0f9439fb340bb82d6000401","tid":2510753,"uid":371815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339a38f1553b1f1a79d3805914d14c1df0d66051","tid":2510753,"uid":371815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f